## 🔴 Lesson: Auto-Doc MUST Run After EVERY Fix (2026-05-30, 19:04 UTC)

**Boss caught that auto_doc_updater.py was NEVER called** after today's P0-P3 work and booking fixes. Despite being in SOUL.md templates, it was skipped on EVERY fix.

**Root Cause:**
- Sub-agent task descriptions didn't include auto-doc as mandatory step
- Kora's post-fix process didn't verify auto-doc was called
- No enforcement mechanism existed

**Fix Applied:**
1. SOUL.md ✅ — Added "🔴 MANDATORY: Auto-Doc After EVERY Fix" with explicit rules
2. SOUL.md ✅ — Every sub-agent task MUST end with auto-doc instructions

**New Rule:** Fix is NOT complete until `auto_doc_updater.py` runs on VPS AND workspace docs are updated. No doc update = fix not done.
